overview: The film revolves around the story of a young man (Saad) working (Nabatchi) at weddings, a person who provides the singers and theatrical paragraphs on stage in the popular celebrations. This young man is looking for an opportunity to realize himself and his dreams, so that he can emerge from the environment in which he and his mother live and marry those he loves, but he faces many problems in order to achieve this.
title: النبطشى
